<Content>Not bad, but not terrific either... The location is not bad, the tram station is near from the hotel, not too much traffic passing by, there's a supermarkt nearby, some restaurants, and the surroundings look actually quite nice. It would be suitable for people who would prefer staying in a more peaceful part of Amsterdam.The room is fine, the staffs are friendly too. But I would advice people not to expect a quality of a 4-star hotel (which they claim to be); this hotel would rather do as an 'above average' 3-star hotel.  
